 - snoop bugs fixed
 - blitter bugs fixed (opponent cars trashed on fast machines)
 - source code included

Notes:

There is no installer.
Just put the "WrongWayDriver" file where the .slave resides 

To run the game just type in a shell where the files are located:

whdload WrongWayDriver.slave PRELOAD

(no need for PRELOAD as there's only one file but it avoids one OS swap)

or use provided icon